var code = {
  "version": 2,
  "type": "kit",
  "title": "torrentdownload.ch",
  "icon": "data:image/png;base64,",
  "desc": "",
  "downloadUrl": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/osokg36/tms/master/TorrentDownload.txt",
  "tVersion": "1.0.1",
  "search": {
    "loginUrl": "",
    "loginFormSelector": "",
    "searchUrl": "https://www.torrentdownload.ch/search?q=%search% ",
    "nextPageSelector": {
      "selector": "#next",
      "attr": "href"
    },
    "baseUrl": "https://www.torrentdownload.ch/",
    "requestType": "GET",
    "listItemSelector": "body>div>table:eq(1)>tbody>tr",
    "listItemSplice": [
      1,
      0
    ],
    "torrentSelector": {
      "categoryTitle": ">td.tdleft>div.tt-name>span",
      "title": ">td.tdleft>div.tt-name>a",
      "url": {
        "selector": ">td.tdleft>div.tt-name>a",
        "attr": "href"
      },
      "size": ">td:eq(2)",
      "downloadUrl": {
        "selector": ">td.tdleft>div.tt-name>a",
        "attr": "href"
      },
      "seed": ">td.tdseed",
      "peer": ">td.tdleech",
      "date": ">td:eq(1)"
    },
    "onGetValue": {
      "size": [
        "convertSize"
      ],
      "date": [
        "replaceToday",
        {
          "name": "timeFormat",
          "format": "4"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "uid": 2049872252
};

API_exKit(code);
